@HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new customer
POST {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "customer1",
  "password": "Password123",
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "birthDate": "1990-01-01",
  "idCard": "1234567890",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "0123456789",
  "address": "123 Main St, City"
}

### Login
POST {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "customer1",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Room Endpoints

### Get all rooms
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Room

### Get available rooms
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Room/available

### Get room by ID
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Room/101

### Create a new room (Admin only)
POST {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Room
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "roomID": "109",
  "roomType": 1
}

### Booking Endpoints

### Get all bookings (Admin/Staff only)
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Booking
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get customer bookings
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Booking/customer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a booking
POST {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Booking
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rooms": [
    {
      "roomID": "101",
      "dateIn": "2025-05-10T14:00:00",
      "dateOut": "2025-05-12T12:00:00"
    }
  ]
}

### Service Endpoints

### Get all services
GET {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Service

### Create a service (Admin only)
POST {{HotelManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Service
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "description": "Room Service",
  "price": 50000
}
